'''Koreya y’Amajyaruguru''' cyangwa '''Koreya ya Ruguru''' ([[igikoreya]]: '''조선민주주의인민공화국''') ni [[igihugu]] muri [[Aziya]]. Umurwa mukuru rw'iki gihugu ni [[Pyongyang]]. Ururimi rwa Koreya y’Amajyaruguru ni igikoreya, ariko kiratandukanye n’icya [[Koreya y’Amajyepfo]] mu kibonezamvugo n’amagambo. Umuyobozi wayo ni [[Kim Jong Un]]. Igihugu gatuwe n’abaturage bagera kuri 25,368,620 (2016), batuye ku buso bwa 120,540km². Koreya y’Amajyaruguru n’iy’Amajyepfo zari ubukoloni bw’Ubuyapani, kugeza aho [[Intambara ya kabiri y’isi]] irangiriye mu [[1945]].


